<h3>3.2 Data Flow</h3>
<p><strong>Write path (Notepad → Sheet):</strong> User types in textarea → parser extracts entries → 2-second debounce → POST sends trip name, currency, all parsed rows, and raw text → Apps Script compares with existing rows → skips matches, updates changes, appends new, deletes extras.</p>
<p><strong>Read path (Sheet → App):</strong> Manual sync button triggers GET with <code>limit=2</code> → Apps Script reads Notes tab (most recent 2 trips) → returns trip name, currency, raw text → frontend merges with localStorage data.</p>
<p><strong>Offline path:</strong> All notepad text saves to localStorage immediately. Sync attempts fail silently. On reconnection, next auto-push sends everything.</p>

