<h2 id="s6">6. Expense Types, Tags & Classification</h2>

<h3>6.1 Three Expense Types</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Type</th><th>Trigger</th><th>Counted in Totals?</th><th>Counted in Day Tally?</th><th>Tag</th><th>Tag Color</th></tr>
<tr><td><span class="badge b-green">Expense</span></td><td>Default (no keyword)</td><td>Yes — Cash or Card box</td><td>Yes</td><td><span class="badge b-blue">cc</span> (if card)</td><td>Blue #185FA5</td></tr>
