<h3>6.2 Tag Rendering</h3>
<p>Tags are rendered as outlined pill badges positioned before the amount value in the summary table:</p>
<pre><code>// Pill tag style (same for cc, atm, dep — only color differs)
{
  fontSize: 9, padding: "2px 6px", borderRadius: 8,
  background: "transparent", border: "1px solid {color}",
  color: "{color}", fontWeight: 500, marginRight: 4,
  display: "inline-flex", alignItems: "center"
}</code></pre>

<h3>6.3 Withdrawal Spelling Tolerance</h3>
<p>The regex <code>/\bwithdr[a]?w[a]?l?\b/i</code> matches: withdrawal, withdrawl, withdrwal, withdral, withdraw. Common misspellings typed quickly on a phone.</p>

<h3>6.4 Google Sheet Type Column</h3>
<p>The Type column in the Expenses sheet stores: <code>Expense</code>, <code>Withdrawal</code>, or <code>Deposit</code>. This enables filtering in sheets/charts.</p>

