<h3>7.2 Three Formatting Functions</h3>

<table>
<tr><th>Function</th><th>Used In</th><th>Behavior</th></tr>
<tr><td><code>fmt(n)</code></td><td>Table entry amounts</td><td>Full number with locale grouping. <code>1,200</code> / <code>23,000</code></td></tr>
<tr><td><code>fmtC(n, code)</code></td><td>Daily totals in table</td><td>Currency symbol + number. K/M only for VND/IDR/KRW at 100K+</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>fmtBox(n, code)</code></td><td>Summary stat boxes only</td><td>Compact, no decimals. Currency-specific abbreviations</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>7.3 fmtBox() Rules by Currency Group</h3>

<p><strong>Indian system (INR, LKR):</strong></p>
<div class="formula">Under 1L → Indian grouping (₹85,000)<br/>1,00,000+ → L format (₹1.2 L, ₹5.3 L, ₹12 L)<br/>1,00,00,000+ → Cr format (₹1 Cr, ₹2.5 Cr)</div>

<p><strong>Western system (USD, EUR, GBP, THB, SGD, MYR, AED, AUD, JPY, PHP):</strong></p>
<div class="formula">Under 10K → full number ($8,500)<br/>10,000+ → K format ($25K, $150K)<br/>1,000,000+ → M format ($2.3M)</div>

<p><strong>Big currencies (VND, IDR, KRW):</strong></p>
<div class="formula">Under 10K → full number (₫8,500)<br/>10,000+ → K format (₫23K, ₫350K)<br/>1,000,000+ → M format (₫2.3M)</div>

